# Zathura document viewer config.

set statusbar-h-padding 0
set statusbar-v-padding 0
set page-padding 1
set selection-clipboard clipboard
set recolor 1
set recolor-keephue 1
set font "monospace normal 16"

# KEYBINDS
## Navigation
map l navigate next
map <Right> navigate next
map <S-Right> navigate next

map h navigate previous
map <Left> navigate previous
map <S-Left> navigate previous

## Scrolling
map j scroll down
map <S-Down> scroll down
map d scroll half-down
map D scroll full-down
map <Down> scroll full-down

map k scroll up
map <S-Up> scroll up
map u scroll half-up
map U scroll full-up
map <Up> scroll full-up

map H scroll left
map L scroll right

## View Modifications
map J zoom in
map K zoom out
map r rotate
map i recolor
map 0 zoom default
map 2 toggle_page_mode


## Modes
map 1 toggle_presentation
map [presentation] 1 toggle_presentation
map [presentation] 2 toggle_page_mode

map 3 toggle_fullscreen
map [fullscreen] 3 toggle_fullscreen
map [fullscreen] 2 toggle_page_mode

map 9 toggle_index
map [index] 9 toggle_index
map [index] 2 toggle_page_mode


## Misc
map R reload
map p print
